---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us — BlocFeed">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-100/40 to-white">
    <br><br><br>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pt-24 pb-16 sm:pb-24 lg:px-8 lg:pt-32 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">
        About BlocFeed
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        BlocFeed is where ideas find momentum. We’re building the first platform that transforms sparks of creativity into real opportunities — connecting innovators, collaborators, and investors in one vibrant ecosystem.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-7">
          At BlocFeed, our mission is simple: <strong>empower creators to share, collaborate, and monetize their ideas</strong>. Too often, brilliant concepts remain hidden in notebooks or lost in conversations. We believe every idea deserves a chance to grow, find partners, and become something bigger.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-7">
          By combining intuitive tools, transparent terms, and a supportive community, we’re creating a launchpad where innovation thrives. Whether you’re a student with a side project, a designer with a vision, or an investor looking for the next big thing — BlocFeed is your home.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="/about-mission.jpg" alt="Our Mission" class="rounded-xl shadow-lg"/>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Core Values</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        These principles guide everything we do — from product design to community engagement.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white shadow-md">
          <div class="text-3xl">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Collaboration</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">We believe the best ideas are built together. BlocFeed fosters partnerships and teamwork.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white shadow-md">
          <div class="text-3xl">💡</div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Creativity</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Innovation starts with imagination. We celebrate originality and bold thinking.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white shadow-md">
          <div class="text-3xl">🛡️</div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Trust</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Transparency and respect are at the heart of our platform. Your ideas remain yours.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-lg bg-white shadow-md">
          <div class="text-3xl">🚀</div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Growth</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">We’re here to help creators scale their visions into sustainable ventures.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-20 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <img src="/about-story.jpg" alt="Our Story" class="rounded-xl shadow-lg"/>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-7">
          BlocFeed was born from a simple frustration: too many great ideas never see the light of day. Our founders — a mix of creators, developers, and entrepreneurs — wanted to change that. They envisioned a platform where ideas could be shared openly, protected fairly, and nurtured into reality.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-7">
          Since our launch, we’ve grown into a global community of innovators. From students sketching their first prototypes to seasoned professionals pitching startups, BlocFeed is proving that when ideas are given space, they flourish.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

